				<title>咖啡价格再度走高：巴西咖啡采收延迟，如何推升生豆成本并传导到中国杯中</title>
				<link>https://www.coffeeprism.com/posts/ka-pei-jie-ge-zai-du-zou-gao-ba-xi-ka-pei-cai-shou/</link>
				<pubDate>Fri, 19 Jun 2026 19:57:14 +0800</pubDate>
